---
import Sidebar from '../../components/sidebar/en/Sidebar.astro';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<style>
  @import '../index.css';
</style>

<Layout lang="en">
  <div class="container">
    <Sidebar />
    <main id="main-content" class="content">
        <h2>Summary</h2>
        <p class="summary">
          For 6 years, I have been a passionate Full-Stack Developer with a focus on web development.
          I enjoy working test-driven and rely on clean and scalable architectures.
          In my free time, I play handball and have been studying Computer Science/IT Security part-time since October 2024.
        </p>

      <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Full-Stack Software Developer</h3>
        <b>10&#8203;/2020 - 07/2025</b>
        <p><i><a href="https://www.brainbirds.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Brainbirds GmbH</a>, Munich</i></p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Full-stack development of a performant web application: reduced loading times by up to 40 % and build times
            by up to 25 % using targeted caching, code splitting, and DNS configurations
          </li>
          <li>API development and integration</li>
          <li>Database administration and testing infrastructure (PostgreSQL, Unit Tests, End-to-End Tests)</li>
          <li>Development and maintenance of software architecture (AWS, Google Cloud Platform, Heroku)</li>
          <li>CI/CD pipelines and DevOps processes (GitHub Actions, Docker)</li>
        </ul>

