          </div>
        </details>

        <h3>Frontend Software Developer</h3>
        <b>04&#8203;/2020 - 10/2020</b>
        <p><i><a href="https://www.myposter.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">myposter GmbH</a>, Munich</i></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Frontend development of a new product-calendar-configurator</li>
          <li>Continuous development of the myposter website</li>
          <li>Quality assurance through unit and end-to-end tests</li>
        </ul>

        <details aria-label="Tech Stack Details for myposter Position">
          <summary>Tech Stack</summary>
          <div>
            <span>Vue.js</span><span>Konva.js</span><span>JavaScript</span><span>SCSS</span><span>Jest</span><span>Cypress</span><span>Storybook</span>
