          </div>
        </details>

        <h3>Junior Software Developer</h3>
        <b>09&#8203;/2016 - 04/2020</b>
        <p><i><a href="https://www.jochen-schweizer.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jochen Schweizer mydays Holding GmbH</a>, Munich</i></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Development of the web presence in Demandware (JavaScript)</li>
          <li>
            Migration of the website to microservices architecture with a 60 % reduction in loading times through
            lazy loading, image optimization, and progressive web app technologies
          </li>
          <li>Responsibility for the partner portal (Perl, Moose, DBIx, Template Toolkit)</li>
          <li>Technical contact person for the partner portal in cross-functional teams</li>
        </ul>

        <details>
          <summary>Tech Stack</summary>
          <div>
            <span>TypeScript</span><span>Node.js</span><span>Perl</span><span>Handlebars</span><span>React.js</span><span>jQuery</span><span>SCSS</span><span>Google Tag Manager</span><span>MySQL</span><span>Sequelize</span><span>Docker</span>
