      </div>

      <h2>Engagement</h2>
      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Voluntary Social Year</h3>
        <b>07&#8203;/2013 - 08/2014</b>
        <p><i>Montessori School, Munich</i></p>
        <p>
          Care and support of seventh graders in an educational village.
          Class assistance in various subjects as well as targeted English tutoring
          in small groups of 2-3 students.
        </p>

        <h3>Volunteer Youth Coach</h3>
        <b>2018 - 2022</b>
        <p><i>TSV Milbertshofen Handball, Munich</i></p>
        <p>
          Training and coaching of youth players (12-16 years).
          Development of leadership skills, teamwork, and
          communication skills through group leadership and conflict management.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
